          logos.travel does not warrant the accuracy, reliability or completeness of any information contained on our sites. To the fullest extent permitted by law, logos.travel, our affiliated companies and/or licensors exclude all liability for any loss or damage suffered by you or any third party whether direct or indirect, incidental or consequential and arising from your use of or access to, or inability to use or access a site, including any loss of data or damage caused by downloading content from our sites.
